---
title: Quickest Mac and Cheese with Spinach, Tomato, and Cheesy Breadcrumbs
description: If you think mac and cheese is just pasta and cheese, think again. Our chefs managed to sneak tomato and spinach into this super speedy comfort dish. But don’t worry—your kids will be too distracted by the crunchiness of the panko breadcrumbs and creaminess of the cheddar cheese to even notice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quickest-mac-and-cheese-2dc3a3ef.jpg
